overview: Investigative journalist and Sky News Australia host Sharri Markson uncovers critical new information and shocking claims about how the COVID-19 pandemic began. Interviewing a range of Chinese whistle-blowers, scientists and high-ranking intelligence officials, 'What Really Happened in Wuhan' brings us closer to discovering the truth of what happened in Wuhan. The documentary is also the first sit-down interview for an Australian broadcast media outlet with former president Donald Trump, since the 2020 US election.
title: What Really Happened in Wuhan
